WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:02.933
Zhao Zixuan, I can't control you anymore

2
00:00:02.933 --> 00:00:05.500
Leave this house today

3
00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:07.800
Dad and son will never dare again

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:09.266
Forgive your son

5
00:00:09.266 --> 00:00:10.266
Don't call me dad

6
00:00:10.333 --> 00:00:11.500
I'm not your dad

7
00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:12.700
You said you were wrong.

8
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:13.700
Where are you sitting?

9
00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:14.800
Tell me about it.

10
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.566
I shouldn't have bought those bottles and jars

11
00:00:17.666 --> 00:00:19.800
As a result, the company's capital turnover is not open

12
00:00:19.800 --> 00:00:21.966
Why did you buy those things?

13
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:24.800
Is it just for your own interest?

14
00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:26.600
You don't even want the company anymore

15
00:00:26.666 --> 00:00:28.766
This company is my heart and soul

16
00:00:28.766 --> 00:00:30.800
Dad is that Xu Tao

17
00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:32.233
I don't want to lose to him.

18
00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:33.933
Don't want to lose to him

19
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.566
So you squander the money.

20
00:00:35.566 --> 00:00:37.066
Ready to get angry with him

21
00:00:37.166 --> 00:00:37.700
How do I

22
00:00:37.700 --> 00:00:40.500
Giving birth to a useless thing like you?

23
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.066
From the moment you accept the company

24
00:00:42.066 --> 00:00:43.666
How much did the company lose?

25
00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:46.366
If I hadn't been behind you to help you wipe your ass

26
00:00:46.366 --> 00:00:48.800
This family has long been defeated by you

27
00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:52.000
God, what have I done?

28
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:53.600
The son is incompetent

29
00:00:53.966 --> 00:00:55.700
You also know that you are incompetent

30
00:00:55.766 --> 00:00:57.066
Now what?

31
00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:58.766
The company's funds cannot be turned around

32
00:00:58.766 --> 00:01:00.366
You really want to bankrupt our family?

33
00:01:00.566 --> 00:01:02.100
Down the street?

34
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:04.500
Dad and son will figure it out

35
00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:07.066
Tell me what you can do

36
00:01:07.533 --> 00:01:09.933
Mengqi is such a good girl, I don't cherish it

37
00:01:09.933 --> 00:01:12.733
Don't think I don't know what you do every day

38
00:01:12.733 --> 00:01:16.200
My life's work has been ruined by you

